---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 155
  - Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Interiorization and Transmutation
    of the Faculties
  - 761
---
A full investigation into Truth will extinguish your desires at once, and the
extinction of desires will restore your mind to rest.
